{
  "video_id": "QuR969uMICM",
  "title": "A beginner's guide to quantum computing | Shohini Ghose",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12917.0,
      "end_time": 14238.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s play a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14825.0,
      "end_time": 17701.0,
      "text": "Imagine that you are in Las Vegas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17725.0,
      "end_time": 19760.0,
      "text": "in a casino,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19100.0,
      "end_time": 23116.0,
      "text": "and you decide to play a game on one of the casino&#39;s computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23140.0,
      "end_time": 25726.0,
      "text": "just like you might play solitaire or chess."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26520.0,
      "end_time": 29669.0,
      "text": "The computer can make moves in the game, just like a human player."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30438.0,
      "end_time": 32137.0,
      "text": "This is a coin game."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32732.0,
      "end_time": 35787.0,
      "text": "It starts with a coin showing heads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35811.0,
      "end_time": 37612.0,
      "text": "and the computer will play first."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37636.0,
      "end_time": 40492.0,
      "text": "It can choose to flip the coin or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40516.0,
      "end_time": 42324.0,
      "text": "but you don&#39;t get to see the outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43144.0,
      "end_time": 44324.0,
      "text": "Next, it&#39;s your turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44862.0,
      "end_time": 47704.0,
      "text": "You can also choose to flip the coin or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47728.0,
      "end_time": 51188.0,
      "text": "and your move will not be revealed to your opponent, the computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51737.0,
      "end_time": 55736.0,
      "text": "Finally, the computer plays again, and can flip the coin or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55760.0,
      "end_time": 58451.0,
      "text": "and after these three rounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58475.0,
      "end_time": 60404.0,
      "text": "the coin is revealed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60428.0,
      "end_time": 63236.0,
      "text": "and if it is heads, the computer wins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 64974.0,
      "text": "if it&#39;s tails, you win."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66210.0,
      "end_time": 67922.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a pretty simple game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67947.0,
      "end_time": 71340.0,
      "text": "and if everybody plays honestly, and the coin is fair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71364.0,
      "end_time": 75126.0,
      "text": "then you have a 50 percent chance of winning this game."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75150.0,
      "end_time": 77424.0,
      "text": "And to confirm that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77448.0,
      "end_time": 80583.0,
      "text": "I asked my students to play this game on our computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80607.0,
      "end_time": 82591.0,
      "text": "and after many, many tries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82615.0,
      "end_time": 86655.0,
      "text": "their winning rate ended up being 50 percent, or close to 50 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86679.0,
      "end_time": 88330.0,
      "text": "as expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88354.0,
      "end_time": 90390.0,
      "text": "Sounds like a boring game, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90414.0,
      "end_time": 93631.0,
      "text": "But what if you could play this game on a quantum computer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94665.0,
      "end_time": 97745.0,
      "text": "Now, Las Vegas casinos do not have quantum computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97769.0,
      "end_time": 99510.0,
      "text": "as far as I know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99534.0,
      "end_time": 102970.0,
      "text": "but IBM has built a working quantum computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102994.0,
      "end_time": 104191.0,
      "text": "Here it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104605.0,
      "end_time": 106890.0,
      "text": "But what is a quantum computer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106534.0,
      "end_time": 109343.0,
      "text": "Well, quantum physics describes"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109367.0,
      "end_time": 113137.0,
      "text": "the behavior of atoms and fundamental particles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 113161.0,
      "end_time": 115644.0,
      "text": "like electrons and photons."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115668.0,
      "end_time": 117392.0,
      "text": "So a quantum computer operates"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117416.0,
      "end_time": 120230.0,
      "text": "by controlling the behavior of these particles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120470.0,
      "end_time": 123713.0,
      "text": "but in a way that is completely different from our regular computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124279.0,
      "end_time": 128174.0,
      "text": "So a quantum computer is not just a more powerful version"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128199.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130304.00000000001,
      "text": "of our current computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130328.0,
      "end_time": 134335.0,
      "text": "just like a light bulb is not a more powerful candle."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134359.0,
      "end_time": 138478.0,
      "text": "You cannot build a light bulb by building better and better candles."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139480.0,
      "end_time": 141263.0,
      "text": "A light bulb is a different technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141287.0,
      "end_time": 143941.0,
      "text": "based on deeper scientific understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143965.0,
      "end_time": 147702.0,
      "text": "Similarly, a quantum computer is a new kind of device,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147726.0,
      "end_time": 150475.0,
      "text": "based on the science of quantum physics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 150499.0,
      "end_time": 153649.0,
      "text": "and just like a light bulb transformed society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153673.0,
      "end_time": 156333.0,
      "text": "quantum computers have the potential to impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156357.0,
      "end_time": 158234.0,
      "text": "so many aspects of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 158258.0,
      "end_time": 162186.0,
      "text": "including our security needs, our health care and even the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 162837.0,
      "end_time": 167137.0,
      "text": "So companies all around the world are working to build these devices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167162.0,
      "end_time": 169497.0,
      "text": "and to see what the excitement is all about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169521.0,
      "end_time": 171671.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s play our game on a quantum computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172862.0,
      "end_time": 177635.0,
      "text": "So I can log into IBM&#39;s quantum computer from right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177659.0,
      "end_time": 180134.0,
      "text": "which means I can play the game remotely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 180158.0,
      "end_time": 181308.0,
      "text": "and so can you."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182151.0,
      "end_time": 187573.0,
      "text": "To make this happen, you may remember getting an email ahead of time, from TED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 187597.0,
      "end_time": 191322.0,
      "text": "asking you whether you would choose to flip the coin or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 191346.0,
      "end_time": 193410.0,
      "text": "if you played the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193650.0,
      "end_time": 197933.0,
      "text": "Well, actually, we asked you to choose between a circle or a square."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 197957.0,
      "end_time": 201799.0,
      "text": "You didn&#39;t know it, but your choice of circle meant \"flip the coin,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201823.0,
      "end_time": 203980.0,
      "text": "and your choice of square was \"don&#39;t flip.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 204723.0,
      "end_time": 207564.0,
      "text": "We received 372 responses."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 207588.0,
      "end_time": 208778.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 208802.0,
      "end_time": 213269.0,
      "text": "That means we can play 372 games against the quantum computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 213294.0,
      "end_time": 214922.0,
      "text": "using your choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 214946.0,
      "end_time": 217191.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a pretty fast game to play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 217215.0,
      "end_time": 219422.0,
      "text": "so I can show you the results right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220231.0,
      "end_time": 222537.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, you didn&#39;t do very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 222561.0,
      "end_time": 224634.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 224658.0,
      "end_time": 227714.0,
      "text": "The quantum computer won almost every game."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228159.0,
      "end_time": 231881.0,
      "text": "It lost a few only because of operational errors in the computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 231905.0,
      "end_time": 233867.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 233891.0,
      "end_time": 237191.0,
      "text": "So how did it achieve this amazing winning streak?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 238224.0,
      "end_time": 240716.0,
      "text": "It seems like magic or cheating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 240741.0,
      "end_time": 243119.0,
      "text": "but actually, it&#39;s just quantum physics in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 243780.0,
      "end_time": 245356.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s how it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 245380.0,
      "end_time": 250832.0,
      "text": "A regular computer simulates heads or tails of a coin as a bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250856.0,
      "end_time": 252511.0,
      "text": "a zero or a one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252535.0,
      "end_time": 256415.0,
      "text": "or a current flipping on and off inside your computer chip."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 256439.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258519.00000000003,
      "text": "A quantum computer is completely different."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259250.0,
      "end_time": 263763.0,
      "text": "A quantum bit has a more fluid, nonbinary identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 264511.0,
      "end_time": 270353.0,
      "text": "It can exist in a superposition, or a combination of zero and one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 270377.0,
      "end_time": 275830.0,
      "text": "with some probability of being zero and some probability of being one."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 275545.0,
      "end_time": 278760.0,
      "text": "In other words, its identity is on a spectrum."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 278790.0,
      "end_time": 282593.0,
      "text": "For example, it could have a 70 percent chance of being zero"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282617.0,
      "end_time": 284953.0,
      "text": "and a 30 percent chance of being one"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284977.0,
      "end_time": 288991.0,
      "text": "or 80-20 or 60-40."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 289160.0,
      "end_time": 291629.0,
      "text": "The possibilities are endless."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 291653.0,
      "end_time": 293190.0,
      "text": "The key idea here"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293430.0,
      "end_time": 297263.0,
      "text": "is that we have to give up on precise values of zero and one"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 297287.0,
      "end_time": 299128.0,
      "text": "and allow for some uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 299737.0,
      "end_time": 301388.0,
      "text": "So during the game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 301412.0,
      "end_time": 306159.0,
      "text": "the quantum computer creates this fluid combination of heads and tails,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306183.0,
      "end_time": 307334.0,
      "text": "zero and one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 307358.0,
      "end_time": 309626.0,
      "text": "so that no matter what the player does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309650.0,
      "end_time": 310837.0,
      "text": "flip or no flip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310862.0,
      "end_time": 313238.0,
      "text": "the superposition remains intact."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 313830.0,
      "end_time": 317306.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of like stirring a mixture of two fluids."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 317714.0,
      "end_time": 322990.0,
      "text": "Whether or not you stir, the fluids remain in a mixture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 322123.0,
      "end_time": 324544.0,
      "text": "but in its final move,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 324568.0,
      "end_time": 328508.0,
      "text": "the quantum computer can unmix the zero and one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 328532.0,
      "end_time": 332270.0,
      "text": "perfectly recovering heads so that you lose every time."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 332294.0,
      "end_time": 333864.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 334267.0,
      "end_time": 337647.0,
      "text": "If you think this is all a bit weird, you are absolutely right."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338608.0,
      "end_time": 342687.0,
      "text": "Regular coins do not exist in combinations of heads and tails."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 343560.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "We do not experience this fluid quantum reality"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 347284.0,
      "end_time": 348754.0,
      "text": "in our everyday lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 349247.0,
      "end_time": 351501.0,
      "text": "So if you are confused by quantum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 351525.0,
      "end_time": 353431.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t worry, you&#39;re getting it."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 353455.0,
      "end_time": 356619.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 356643.0,
      "end_time": 360899.0,
      "text": "But even though we don&#39;t experience quantum strangeness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 360923.0,
      "end_time": 364810.0,
      "text": "we can see its very real effects in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 364105.0,
      "end_time": 365859.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve seen the data for yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 366529.0,
      "end_time": 367990.0,
      "text": "The quantum computer won"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 368140.0,
      "end_time": 372802.0,
      "text": "because it harnessed superposition and uncertainty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 372826.0,
      "end_time": 375182.0,
      "text": "and these quantum properties are powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 375206.0,
      "end_time": 377484.0,
      "text": "not just to win coin games,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377508.0,
      "end_time": 381126.0,
      "text": "but also to build future quantum technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 381150.0,
      "end_time": 384666.0,
      "text": "So let me give you three examples of potential applications"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 384690.0,
      "end_time": 386150.0,
      "text": "that could change our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387147.0,
      "end_time": 392448.0,
      "text": "First of all, quantum uncertainty could be used to create private keys"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392472.0,
      "end_time": 396262.0,
      "text": "for encrypting messages sent from one location to another"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396286.0,
      "end_time": 401415.0,
      "text": "so that hackers could not secretly copy the key perfectly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 401439.0,
      "end_time": 402992.0,
      "text": "because of quantum uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 403809.0,
      "end_time": 407595.0,
      "text": "They would have to break the laws of quantum physics"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 407619.0,
      "end_time": 408888.0,
      "text": "to hack the key."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 409531.0,
      "end_time": 414405.0,
      "text": "So this kind of unbreakable encryption is already being tested by banks"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 414429.0,
      "end_time": 416364.0,
      "text": "and other institutions worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 417357.0,
      "end_time": 422806.0,
      "text": "Today, we use more than 17 billion connected devices globally."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 423619.0,
      "end_time": 427119.0,
      "text": "Just imagine the impact quantum encryption could have in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428171.0,
      "end_time": 433901.0,
      "text": "Secondly, quantum technologies could also transform health care and medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434427.0,
      "end_time": 439728.0,
      "text": "For example, the design and analysis of molecules for drug development"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 439752.0,
      "end_time": 442147.0,
      "text": "is a challenging problem today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 442171.0,
      "end_time": 447123.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s because exactly describing and calculating"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 447147.0,
      "end_time": 451248.0,
      "text": "all of the quantum properties of all the atoms in the molecule"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 451273.0,
      "end_time": 454924.0,
      "text": "is a computationally difficult task, even for our supercomputers."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 455480.0,
      "end_time": 457686.0,
      "text": "But a quantum computer could do better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 457710.0,
      "end_time": 460964.0,
      "text": "because it operates using the same quantum properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 460988.0,
      "end_time": 463540.0,
      "text": "as the molecule it&#39;s trying to simulate."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 463564.0,
      "end_time": 468341.0,
      "text": "So future large-scale quantum simulations for drug development"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 468365.0,
      "end_time": 471651.0,
      "text": "could perhaps lead to treatments for diseases like Alzheimer&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 471675.0,
      "end_time": 473817.0,
      "text": "which affects thousands of lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 474355.0,
      "end_time": 477392.0,
      "text": "And thirdly, my favorite quantum application"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 477416.0,
      "end_time": 482750.0,
      "text": "is teleportation of information from one location to another"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 482990.0,
      "end_time": 485140.0,
      "text": "without physically transmitting the information."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 485847.0,
      "end_time": 489275.0,
      "text": "Sounds like sci-fi, but it is possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 489300.0,
      "end_time": 493190.0,
      "text": "because these fluid identities of the quantum particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 493430.0,
      "end_time": 496401.0,
      "text": "can get entangled across space and time"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 496425.0,
      "end_time": 500350.0,
      "text": "in such a way that when you change something about one particle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 500590.0,
      "end_time": 501515.0,
      "text": "it can impact the other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 501539.0,
      "end_time": 504197.0,
      "text": "and that creates a channel for teleportation."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 505390.0,
      "end_time": 507647.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s already been demonstrated in research labs"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 507672.0,
      "end_time": 510593.0,
      "text": "and could be part of a future quantum internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 511219.0,
      "end_time": 514566.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have such a network as yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 514590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517494.00000000006,
      "text": "but my team is working on these possibilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 517518.0,
      "end_time": 521367.0,
      "text": "by simulating a quantum network on a quantum computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 522520.0,
      "end_time": 526500.0,
      "text": "So we have designed and implemented some interesting new protocols"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 526740.0,
      "end_time": 531756.0,
      "text": "such as teleportation among different users in the network"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 531780.0,
      "end_time": 534200.0,
      "text": "and efficient data transmission"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 535628.0,
      "text": "and even secure voting."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 536502.0,
      "end_time": 539381.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a lot of fun for me, being a quantum physicist."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 539405.0,
      "end_time": 540898.0,
      "text": "I highly recommend it."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 540922.0,
      "end_time": 542880.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 542904.0,
      "end_time": 545785.0,
      "text": "We get to be explorers in a quantum wonderland."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 545809.0,
      "end_time": 548693.0,
      "text": "Who knows what applications we will discover next."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 549222.0,
      "end_time": 552470.0,
      "text": "We must tread carefully and responsibly"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 552710.0,
      "end_time": 554700.0,
      "text": "as we build our quantum future."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 554809.0,
      "end_time": 556607.0,
      "text": "And for me, personally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 556631.0,
      "end_time": 562100.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t see quantum physics as a tool just to build quantum computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 562124.0,
      "end_time": 567258.0,
      "text": "I see quantum computers as a way for us to probe the mysteries of nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 567282.0,
      "end_time": 571194.0,
      "text": "and reveal more about this hidden world outside of our experiences."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 571218.0,
      "end_time": 573319.0,
      "text": "How amazing that we humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 573344.0,
      "end_time": 576336.0,
      "text": "with our relatively limited access to the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 576360.0,
      "end_time": 578994.0,
      "text": "can still see far beyond our horizons"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 579180.0,
      "end_time": 581598.0,
      "text": "just using our imagination and our ingenuity."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 582211.0,
      "end_time": 584528.0,
      "text": "And the universe rewards us"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 584552.0,
      "end_time": 588480.0,
      "text": "by showing us how incredibly interesting and surprising it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 589171.0,
      "end_time": 592547.0,
      "text": "The future is fundamentally uncertain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 592571.0,
      "end_time": 595750.0,
      "text": "and to me, that is certainly exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 596344.0,
      "end_time": 597495.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 597519.0,
      "end_time": 603626.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}